BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Jw1WbzKgiXZGjtZSzJ2DR
SUMMARY:The Crocodile Presents: Soda Blonde\, guests
DTSTAMP:20260315T214144Z
DTSTART:20260928T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $22.50 ($30.90 after fees)\n\nDay of: $25 ($33.48 afte
	r fees)\n\nSoda Blonde:\n\nSoda Blonde are a four-piece alt-pop band from 
	Dublin\, Ireland\, formed in 2019 by Faye O’Rourke (vocals)\, Adam O’Regan
	 (guitar/keys)\, Donagh Seaver-O’Leary (bass) and Dylan Lynch (drums). The
	 group emerged from the ashes of critically acclaimed indie rock outfit Li
	ttle Green Cars\, moving toward a bolder\, more cinematic and emotionally 
	charged sound that blends evocative lyrics with adventurous production.\n\
	nTheir music traverses the tension between introspection and ambition\, pa
	iring O’Rourke’s distinctive\, expressive vocals with genre-defying arrang
	ements that draw comparisons to synth-infused art-pop and emotionally hone
	st songwriting. Soda Blonde’s debut single “Swimming Through the Night” im
	mediately marked a stylistic shift for the members\, establishing the band
	’s commitment to cinematic hooks and atmospheric grooves.\n\nThe band’s fi
	rst studio album Small Talk (2021) showcased polished\, self-produced song
	writing and was nominated for the Choice Music Prize. Their sophomore reco
	rd Dream Big (2023) expanded their sonic palette and solidified their repu
	tation as one of Ireland’s most compelling contemporary acts. In 2025\, So
	da Blonde released the People Pleaser EP and completed an ambitious live o
	rchestral project with the National Symphony Orchestra at Dublin’s Nationa
	l Concert Hall\, captured in both a concert film and a live album.\n\nKnow
	n for their emotionally charged live performances\, bold visuals and genre
	-spanning sound\, Soda Blonde continue to push beyond conventional pop bou
	ndaries while maintaining a deeply personal connection to their lyrics and
	 visual storytelling.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+
	 bar and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://lin
	k.dice.fm/Bb05d4b1c91d\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/Bb05d4b1c91d
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
